column2: public static int max(int[] array) { int max = array[0]; for (int i = 1; i < array.length; i++) { if (array[i] > max) { max = array[i]; } } return max; }

public static int factorial(int n) { if (n == 0) return 1; else return n * factorial(n-1); }
